---
pagination:
  data: books
  size: 1
  alias: book
permalink: "/books/{{ book.slug }}.txt"
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
# {{ book.title | safe }}{% if book.subtitle %}: {{ book.subtitle | safe }}{% endif %}

- **Author:** {{ book.authors | joinNames | safe }}
{%- if book.isUpcoming %}
- **Status:** Upcoming — Meeting {{ book.meetingDate | monthYear }}
{%- else %}
- **Read:** {{ book.meetingDate | monthYear }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.topic %}
- **Topic:** {{ book.topic | safe }}{% if book.fiction %} (Fiction){% endif %}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.subjectTags and book.subjectTags.length %}
- **Subjects:** {{ book.subjectTags | join(", ") | safe }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.publicationYear %}
- **Published:** {{ book.publicationYear }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.pageCount %}
- **Pages:** {{ book.pageCount }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.pickerNames and book.pickerNames.length %}
- **Picked by:** {{ book.pickerNames | joinNames | safe }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.isbn13 %}
- **ISBN-13:** {{ book.isbn13 }}
{%- endif %}
{%- set clubR = reviews | clubRating(book.slug) %}
{%- if clubR %}
- **Club rating:** {{ clubR.avg }}/5 (from {{ clubR.count }} member{% if clubR.count != 1 %}s{% endif %})
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.olKey %}
- **Open Library:** https://openlibrary.org{{ book.olKey }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.hasCover and book.coverWidths %}
- **Cover:** {{ site.url }}/assets/images/covers/{{ book.slug }}-{{ book.coverWidths[book.coverWidths.length - 1] }}.jpg
{%- endif %}
- **Canonical page:** {{ site.url }}/books/{{ book.slug }}/
{% if book.synopsis %}
## Synopsis

{{ book.synopsis | stripHtml | safe }}
{% endif %}
{%- if book.meetingNotes %}
## Meeting notes

{{ book.meetingNotes | stripHtml | safe }}
{% endif %}
{%- set bookReviews = reviews | reviewsForBook(book.slug) -%}
{% if bookReviews.length %}
## Reviews
{% for r in bookReviews %}
- {{ r.reviewers[0].name if r.reviewers.length else "Anonymous" }}{% if r.rating %} — {{ r.rating }}/5{% endif %}{% if r.dnf %} (Did Not Finish){% endif %}{% if r.wouldRecommend %} — Would recommend{% endif %}{% if r.discussionQuality %} — Discussion quality: {{ r.discussionQuality }}/5{% endif %}
{%- if r.review %}
  {{ r.review | stripHtml | safe }}
{%- endif %}
{%- if r.favoriteQuote %}
  Favorite quote: "{{ r.favoriteQuote | stripHtml | safe }}"
{%- endif %}
{% endfor %}
{%- endif %}
{%- if book.related and book.related.length %}
## Related books
{% for rel in book.related %}
{%- set rbook = null %}
{%- for b in books %}{% if b.slug == rel.slug %}{% set rbook = b %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
{%- if rbook %}
- {{ rbook.title | safe }} ({{ rel.reason | safe }})
  {{ site.url }}/books/{{ rbook.slug }}.txt
{%- endif %}
{%- endfor %}
{%- endif %}
